data.text:
Superhero: Waffleman

Secret Identity: John McBain

Super Powers: Investigative skills, brooding, rocking the facial hair thing, brooding, ability to dangle two hot girls for months on end

Kryptonite: Commitment

Archenemies: His father’s killer and wedding planners

Sweetheart: Natalie Buchanan, no, Evangeline Williamson, no, Natalie, no, Vangie, no, no, Natalie, seriously. That’s it. Natalie.

Superhero: Soulman

Secret Identity: Michael McBain

Super Powers: Practicing medicine, hosting the spirit of the late Al Holden, holding one heck of a Valentine’s Day celebration for his sweetheart

Kryptonite: Body snatchers

Archenemies: The man who killed his father and Dr. Long, the former chief of staff at Llanview Hospital

Sweetheart: Wife Marcie Walsh McBain

Superhero: Lord of the Ring

Secret Identity: Cristian Vega

Super Powers: Painting, bilingual, ability to float like a butterfly and sting like a bee

Kryptonite: TKOs

Archenemy: Carlo Hesser

Sweetheart: Evangeline Williamson, natch

Superhero: Captain Banter

Secret Identity: David Vickers

Super Powers: Charm, wit, scamming, editing, freeloading, blackmail, living the good life, limitless bon mots

Kryptonite: An honest day’s work

Archenemy: Brother Dr. Spencer Truman, sort of

Sweethearts: Aside from himself, you mean? Okay, ex-fiancée Dorian Lord

Superhero: The Ambiguous Avenger

Secret Identity: Spencer Truman

Super Powers: Practicing medicine, ironic last name, orchestrating cover-ups, blackmail, ability to maybe try to convince us that he’s not a villain, after all, thwarting the death penalty like you would not believe

Kryptonite: The truth

Archenemies: Todd Manning, Starr Manning, Kevin Buchanan, anybody who gets in his way, but surprisingly not überscoundrel R.J. Gannon.

Sweetheart: He thinks it’s Blair Manning….
